    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>01 Bedroom size is very spacious with 60 square meters. Generously sized and    delightfully inviting, executive experience the goes far The spacious bedroom   has a king-sized bed and a 32" TV while the separate living area boasts a       private balcony and a fully outfitted kitchen. An elegant luxury room, the      apartment is both comfortable and stylish, making it an excellent long stay     apartment for couples or individuals looking for luxury lodging in Bangkok.</Text>
  </Description>
